From:

Subject: RE: tomorrow 
Date: Thu, 22 Apr 2021 22:12:03 +0000 
Attachments: 2021.04.19_Scheduling_Order.pdf 
Hi 
Attached is the scheduling order with the public dial in information (there is no video). In addition to the public access 
line, the Court has set up a different access line for victims who want to attend-- if you'd like me to, I can let the Court 
know you plan to dial in, so that I can send you the victim access line. Just let me know your preference. 
Thanks, 
From 
Sent: Thurs ay, Apr' 2  , 1 :  5 PM 
To: 
Subject: tomorrow 
can you send me the link to watch tomorrow's hearing? Thanks.
